<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xml:lang="ko"><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="3.9.2">Jekyll</generator><link href="http://localhost:4000/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" /><link href="http://localhost:4000/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" hreflang="ko" /><updated>2022-06-30T16:37:25+09:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/feed.xml</id><title type="html">Vanilla Page</title><subtitle>repository for learning</subtitle><author><name>vanilla page</name></author><entry><title type="html">Scroll Lock</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/javascript-module/2022/06/30/scroll-lock.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Scroll Lock" /><published>2022-06-30T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-06-30T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/javascript-module/2022/06/30/scroll-lock</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/javascript-module/2022/06/30/scroll-lock.html">&lt;p&gt;업무마다 상이하지만 크게 2가지 유형으로 scroll lock을 적용&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A. body 에 fixed 스타일 적용&lt;br /&gt;
B. body, wrap 등 스크롤 가능 영역에 관련 이벤트 중단&lt;/p&gt;

